Comment: 0,0:09:53.00,0:09:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,~~~START~~~
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.00,0:09:58.66,Ena,,0,0,0,,Welcome to ProSeka AfterTalk "Colors of Pure Sense" Edition!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.28,0:10:06.00,Ena,,0,0,0,,This is Minori Suzuki, voice of Ena Shinonome from Nightcord at 25:00!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.00,0:10:13.23,Ena,,0,0,0,,In these ProSeka AfterTalks, we look back at the events while covering messages you, the fans, have sent in.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.23,0:10:16.68,Ena,,0,0,0,,This time, we'll be covering the "Colors of Pure Sense" event.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.68,0:10:20.79,Ena,,0,0,0,,Did you enjoy the story, everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.79,0:10:23.49,Ena,,0,0,0,,Thank you for reading, and for coming to the Kanshasai, if you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.49,0:10:29.92,Ena,,0,0,0,,Between that and the movie stage greetings, we've busy with lots of chances to meet everyone live.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.92,0:10:32.92,Ena,,0,0,0,,And right after all that, we have an Ena event going on.
